Recommends: ffmpeg, p7zip-full, rclone
Description: Production-grade C++23 Telegram mirror/leech bot
 CMLB downloads URLs, magnet links, and torrents via aria2c or qBittorrent
 and uploads the results back to Telegram or to cloud storage
 (Google Drive, rclone remotes). It supports RSS subscriptions,
 archive extraction, media processing, and a four-tier permission model.
 .
 Built on TDLib, Boost.Asio C++20 coroutines, and SQLite (WAL mode).
